@node "HISTORY" "History"
@TOC USAGE
 @{b}History@{ub}
 @{b}v1.0 - 08 September 1996@{ub}
     · First release.

 @{b}v1.1 - 12 September 1996@{ub}
     · Fixed WBIcon loading problem
     · Removed external WBIcon loading program from StartupPlus & Prefs
     · No longer have to have a window at startupp time
     · Added Ask Window
     · Added More Tooltypes

 @{b}V1.11 - 01 October 1996@{ub}
     · Only Mark Ritter got a copy to test.

 @{b}v1.2 - 28 October 1996@{ub}
     · No changes to the main program.

 @{b}v1.3 - 10 January 1997@{ub}
     · No longer activates the window at startup.
     · Increased icon display size to: width 90 pixels and height 66
       pixels

 @{b}v1.4 - 21 February 1997@{ub}
     · Added a menu bar to make editing the MUI Interface easier.
     · Reimplemented the Ask window and fixed all the bugs that came
       with it
     · Major over haul on the code.
     · Faster Execution. If you want even faster execution disable
       the window
