       DOSPath.library

 @{b}v1.5 - 1 September 1997@{ub}
     · Changed the look of the GUI (MUI)
     · Improved the Error handeling
     · Changed the Keyfile
     · Added wildcard handeling to only locate SUP datafiles
     · Now Compiled in SAS C 5.57
@endnode

